SUMMARY:Build one full response in your next conversation
DESCRIPTION:In your next conversation\, work through the full loop: acknow
 ledge the concern first\, add one useful perspective from the workshop (in
 flation\, compounding\, volatility or time in market)\, then end with one 
 clear\, practical next step. Keep it simple — one insight\, one example\
 , one takeaway.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT15M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Build one full response in your next conversation
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
