SUMMARY:Keep one habit and reinforce the core message
DESCRIPTION:Choose one behaviour to keep as part of your standard client p
 reparation — a better discovery question\, a strong metaphor\, or always
  ending with a next step. Use a resource to reconnect clients to their lon
 g-term goals and reinforce the workshop's core message: staying invested m
 atters more than trying to time every move.
